Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Agent Communication - Multicast System
Production-ready multicast communication framework for efficient group communication
with membership management, reliable delivery, and network optimization.

Advanced features include:
- Dynamic multicast group management with membership protocols
- Hierarchical group structures with nested group support
- Reliable multicast with ordering and duplicate detection
- Network-aware delivery optimization with tree-based routing
- Group discovery and auto-joining based on interests
- Leader election and consensus protocols for group coordination
- Message aggregation and batching for efficiency
- Adaptive group size management with split/merge operations
- Geographic and logical group partitioning
- Comprehensive group analytics and health monitoring
:End Note

Type called "MulticastGroup":
    group_id as String
    name as String
    description as String
    group_type as String
    created_time as Float
    creator_id as String
    leader_id as Optional[String]
